DB2 is a major relational database system on IBM main frames, it has over six thousand licenses over the world to support a very large number of major applications for customer business, Optimizer in DB2 is a critical component for the query processing, it inherited system R technologies and has been improved in very many aspects from numerous valuable real life experiences on customer applications. The major DB2 optimizer enhancements will be discussed with the backgrounds and examples. A wish list for future enhancements as well as some trend and direction of DB2 optimizer will also be discussed.